data.description: Elegantly appointed 4 bed/2.5 bath home in highly sought after Haryan Farms neighborhood. This home has it all, inviting two story entrance, sunny dining room, living room. Newly updated kitchen with island has quartz countertop, new SS appliances, plenty of space for a table and it opens to a sunroom with views of the yard and pond. Family room with plenty of sunlight has a gas starter fireplace. Newly finished basement offers plenty of space for the family to spread out. New hot water heater. First floor laundry room with new washer and dryer. Easy Commute for Metra, close to shopping and restaurants and located in award winning school district 46/127.
